    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based, <strong>hob-safe</strong> <strong>oven-proof casserole dish </strong>with a matching lid with a knob of <strong>butter </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-low heat</p><p>Add the <strong>basmati rice</strong>, <strong>hoisin sauce</strong>, <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong>, <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong> and the <strong>remaining tamari soy sauce</strong> to the dish and give everything a good mix up</p>",
